	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">There are alot of good upgrades out there for reasonable prices these days.  As you approach 60 and then 65, I'd suggest trying to look for pieces with higher +hp/mana on them say 50 or greater to start.  I'm sure someone else will post you a nice list of items to look for.  For starters I'd suggest that you buy yourself a Tainted Heartstone charm, it's a very reasonably priced charm with pretty nice stats, recommended level 60 so you'll get almost maximum benefit from it right away. <img src="images/smilies/smile.gif" border="0" alt="Smile"></font></p>
	
